v1.1.0.0 v1.1.0:\par
\pard{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}{\*\pn\pnlvlblt\pnf1\pnindent0{\pntxtb\'B7}}\nowidctlpar\fi-200\li200 Gamepad support (only for Windows as far as I could test). It includes smooth movement with joysticks.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Deleted Android virtual d-pad... :(\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Added Android virtual joystick! :3\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Screenshots can be taken by pressing f2.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Now you can change between fullscreen, a 480x270 window, a 960x540 window and a 1340x810 window by pressing f5.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}Changed how almost everything works just for optimization and to make the game more similar to MegaMan (1). There are big changes all over the game. These are the most important:\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab Removed opening screen and changed title and stage select screens just to match the original first MegaMan for NES. They will return soon ;).\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab Controls now show up after title screen and before select screen.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab Tweaked stars speed and spawnrate.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab Enhanced controls. Now you don't have to choose between using arrows or "wasd" at the titlescreen.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab Improved diagonal movement. Now you don't move x pixels right and x pixels up when pressing up and right (for example) but sin(45) x pixels right and sin(45) x pixels up. Thanks, Mathematics.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab Imrpoved autofire by a little bit.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab Now you can select stage by taping on the enemy you wanna fight. Only for android.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab Changed SOMETHING.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab Tweacked a lot of values (speed, health, damage and power ammo...) for balance. Almost everything has slightly changed.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab Enhanced the way you change weapons by A LOT. Old HUD: it was nice to meet you. Now, goodbye. By the way, you looked awful. :).\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab Pressing O and P (L and R on android, both shoulders in a gamepad) at the same time transform you back into the default megaship anytime.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab Tweacked some texts.\par
{\pntext\f1\'B7\tab}\tab A lot more changes that shouldn't be appreciable.\par
\pard\nowidctlpar\par
